{"tid":554131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"F.2南亞男生校園遇襲　警帶走同鄉同學助查","createTime":"2018-02-08T08:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-08T12:15:28.000Z","uid":122,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fedbda1711cb2b2dc32baa9831a430b709babf96","tid":554131,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T08:09:04.000Z","msg":"F.2南亞男生校園遇襲　警帶走同鄉同學助查<br />\n<br />\n葵涌中二男生學校內被打受傷。現場為葵合街一間中學，上午11時許，一名南亞裔中二男生在轉堂時，疑被另一名南亞同學打傷，校方報警處理。救護員到場將咀部受傷男生送仁濟醫院治理。警方經初步調查，帶走一名涉嫌傷人同學。"},{"pid":"dc87dc56d9a57c538faa1dc1a597fd60f4b145dd","tid":554131,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T08:12:22.000Z","msg":"伍少梅？"},{"pid":"eeff85c10419c0a47429bdcfc83f5d13593f16da","tid":554131,"uid":6439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc87dc56d9a57c538faa1dc1a597fd60f4b145dd","tid":554131,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T08:12:22.000Z","msg":"伍少梅？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T08:25:28.000Z","msg":"成間學校都係蝻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b1713fd6765a270a6c600a4942a480b1d76b61","tid":554131,"uid":38216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T08:34:43.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗"},{"pid":"eba126ba5a6507fcfae4af26c682cd200bef4005","tid":554131,"uid":102096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T08:37:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d07b78f1c4762d8b98d22c53042028ef4e6bdf9","tid":554131,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeff85c10419c0a47429bdcfc83f5d13593f16da","tid":554131,"uid":6439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc87dc56d9a57c538faa1dc1a597fd60f4b145dd","tid":554131,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T08:12:22.000Z","msg":"伍少梅？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T08:25:28.000Z","msg":"成間學校都係蝻<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma